description: NOTICE OF PROPOSED PROCUREMENT (NPP) For TASK BASED INFORMATICS PROFESSIONAL SERVICES (TBIPS)Reference Number:20221348Organization Name:Office of the Superintendent of Financial Institutions (OSFI)Anticipated Start Date:2023-04-03Contract Duration:The contract period will be from the date of contract award to March 31st, 2024, with irrevocable options to extend it for up to four (4) additional one-year periods.Number of Contracts:1Requirement DetailsTendering Procedure: Selective TenderingThis requirement is open only to those TBIPS Supply Arrangement Holders who qualified under Tier 1 for services in the Greater Toronto Area for multiple categories under Stream 4 and 5: Business Services and Project Management Services, as follows: P.5 Project Executive, P.1 Change Management Consultant, P.12 Risk Management Specialist, B.3 Business Consultant, B.5 Business Process Re-engineering Consultant, and B.7 Business Transformation Architect.The following SA Holders have been invited to submit a proposal:Accenture IncArchipelago Alliance IncBDO Canada LLPCGI Information Systems and Management Consultants IncErnst & Young LLPExcel Human Resources IncFujitsu Consulting (CANADA) IncIBM Canada Limited:KPMG LLP
